WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 30=

01:38.740 --> 01:39.660
Young Master,

01:39.660 --> 01:40.500
this time,

01:40.740 --> 01:43.380
Miss Cai took seven lashes
of the Python Whip.

01:44.290 --> 01:45.570
Though her life is not in danger,

01:45.980 --> 01:47.130
such wounds

01:47.490 --> 01:48.850
require time to heal.

01:49.740 --> 01:51.740
Lord Qi has also placed Miss Cai
under confinement

01:51.740 --> 01:55.210
in the Realm Cavern
of Thousandfold Cliff,

01:55.900 --> 01:57.540
punishing her to reflect for a year.

01:59.020 --> 02:00.050
During this year,

02:00.980 --> 02:02.260
only Song Yuzhi

02:02.570 --> 02:03.690
may enter and leave

02:03.980 --> 02:04.900
to look after her.

02:06.850 --> 02:07.850
If it's him,

02:09.660 --> 02:11.660
he'll surely care for her
with utmost devotion.

02:12.130 --> 02:13.170
Young Master,

02:13.430 --> 02:14.290
you and Miss Cai...

02:14.290 --> 02:15.340
From now on,

02:16.010 --> 02:16.990
we go our separate ways.

02:17.980 --> 02:19.940
From this day forward,

02:19.940 --> 02:22.100
no one in the sect is
to speak of her again.

02:28.290 --> 02:29.130
Yes.

02:41.500 --> 02:42.340
Take

02:43.010 --> 02:43.850
this luminous pearl.

02:44.380 --> 02:45.399
You're afraid of the dark.

02:45.890 --> 02:46.980
With it,

02:47.690 --> 02:50.940
you can at least sleep peacefully.

03:28.170 --> 03:29.010
Zhao,

03:30.170 --> 03:31.010
it's time to eat.

03:31.380 --> 03:33.380
Yuzhi, you're early today.

03:33.730 --> 03:34.980
I'm not hungry yet.

03:35.780 --> 03:36.620
It's back to you.

03:46.260 --> 03:47.100
True.

03:47.820 --> 03:49.170
What if I run out of money again?

03:55.220 --> 03:57.340
The Python Whip wounds
will only heal slowly.

03:57.890 --> 03:59.290
Zhao, you must be careful as well.

04:00.010 --> 04:00.890
I'm fine.

04:01.850 --> 04:03.610
As long as I don't move,
it doesn't hurt.

04:05.610 --> 04:06.690
This was sent by Lord Zhou.

04:06.690 --> 04:08.170
It relieves pain and promotes healing.

04:10.540 --> 04:12.410
I injured Uncle Zhou before.

04:13.730 --> 04:15.170
Yet he still worries about me.

04:15.660 --> 04:17.290
Lord Zhou knows you didn't mean it.

04:17.580 --> 04:18.810
He said his injuries are

04:19.220 --> 04:20.060
nothing serious.

04:21.930 --> 04:23.580
Uncle Zhou wants to ask

04:24.900 --> 04:26.540
about Aunt and Mu Zhengyang, right?

04:29.050 --> 04:30.730
Aunt did once care for Mu Zhengyang.

04:31.410 --> 04:32.580
But after his death,

04:34.220 --> 04:35.060
she never

04:36.170 --> 04:38.140
spoke another word of it.

04:39.250 --> 04:41.250
She must've let it go.

04:41.930 --> 04:43.410
There is nothing more to say.

04:44.700 --> 04:46.610
Her longing faded just like that.

04:48.220 --> 04:49.700
Ms. Cai was carefree,

04:50.050 --> 04:50.890
but

04:51.340 --> 04:52.180
their paths diverged,

04:52.700 --> 04:54.340
so it was a fleeting dream.

04:57.810 --> 04:58.650
Yuzhi,

04:58.900 --> 05:00.340
next time you visit,

05:00.730 --> 05:02.980
bring me some paper and ink.

05:03.930 --> 05:04.770
Sure.

05:05.290 --> 05:07.410
Why suddenly decide to leave?

05:10.610 --> 05:12.250
I've thought about it for a long time.

05:14.540 --> 05:16.170
I used to be immature.

05:17.220 --> 05:18.100
From now on,

05:19.250 --> 05:21.610
I want to become a daughter
whom you're proud of.

05:24.020 --> 05:25.930
I never understood before

05:26.580 --> 05:28.780
why you cared more
for the people of Luoying Valley

05:28.780 --> 05:30.020
than for me.

05:30.700 --> 05:32.346
Was it because my martial arts
were poor,

05:33.250 --> 05:34.250
or because

05:35.370 --> 05:36.780
you didn't care for Mother?

05:39.900 --> 05:41.170
But now, I understand.

05:41.700 --> 05:43.340
As leader of the Six Sects,

05:44.050 --> 05:45.576
you must place the greater good first.

05:45.660 --> 05:46.930
You can't focus only on family.

05:47.540 --> 05:49.346
Ms. Cai sacrificed herself
for the Six Sects.

05:50.100 --> 05:51.780
If you didn't care for her family,

05:51.780 --> 05:53.540
wouldn't that chill the hearts of all?

05:53.930 --> 05:55.730
As your daughter,

05:57.370 --> 05:58.980
I should ease his burdens.

05:59.370 --> 06:01.170
Yet instead, I grew jealous

06:01.540 --> 06:02.380
and caused trouble.

06:03.100 --> 06:04.290
I was truly wrong.

06:07.610 --> 06:08.700
All these years,

06:08.700 --> 06:10.730
I've indeed neglected you.

06:12.700 --> 06:13.850
In my heart,

06:15.020 --> 06:16.290
I feel guilt.

06:21.220 --> 06:23.100
It's my problem.

06:28.730 --> 06:30.810
(Pillar of Jianghu)
I know my aptitude is poor.

06:31.220 --> 06:33.250
It's hard for me to achieve much
in martial arts.

06:33.580 --> 06:35.140
But as a member of the Six Sects,

06:35.140 --> 06:36.810
I can't hide on this mountain

06:37.170 --> 06:38.340
just because I can't fight.

06:39.020 --> 06:40.020
This time,

06:41.140 --> 06:42.810
I wish to follow Ms. Cai's example,

06:43.250 --> 06:44.170
uphold justice,

06:45.050 --> 06:46.383
and bring glory to the Six Sects.

06:48.050 --> 06:51.050
I don't wish you to become like Ms. Cai.

06:51.410 --> 06:52.580
Jianghu is dangerous.

06:53.170 --> 06:54.290
I only hope

06:54.290 --> 06:56.490
you can live this life in peace and joy

06:57.490 --> 06:59.540
by my side.

07:08.540 --> 07:10.780
So, you do care for me.

07:11.370 --> 07:13.810
Then I must not remain weak and useless.

07:18.850 --> 07:21.220
Ever since Zhao was confined,

07:21.220 --> 07:23.370
Qingque Sect hasn't been as lively.

07:25.340 --> 07:26.180
Is she any better?

07:26.490 --> 07:27.780
Seven lashes of the Python Whip.

07:28.220 --> 07:29.490
Injuries to sinew and bone

07:29.490 --> 07:30.660
don't heal so quickly.

07:30.660 --> 07:32.100
It's good enough that she's awakened.

07:33.476 --> 07:35.509
We just sold the first batch
of golden silk armor.

07:35.660 --> 07:37.850
These insect repellent samples
must be sent down asap.

07:38.320 --> 07:40.580
There's still much unfinished business
waiting for Zhao.

07:40.580 --> 07:41.420
Enough.

07:42.410 --> 07:44.660
We haven't even practiced,
yet we are all helping you.

07:44.660 --> 07:45.946
And you keep talking about Zhao.

07:45.957 --> 07:47.340
Enough of that. Let's go.

07:47.340 --> 07:48.180
Lingbo,

07:49.020 --> 07:50.246
Fan is doing this for everyone.

07:50.540 --> 07:52.220
Master donated the money
left by Lord Yin

07:52.220 --> 07:53.060
to Jiangdong

07:53.700 --> 07:55.293
and waived the fees for outer disciples.

07:55.700 --> 07:57.370
If not for Fan managing things,

07:57.370 --> 07:58.540
the sect wouldn't be running.

07:59.160 --> 08:00.050
Just doing my duty.

08:00.050 --> 08:00.890
My duty.

08:02.050 --> 08:03.980
If Zhao hadn't been confined,

08:03.980 --> 08:05.900
we wouldn't be so short of funds.

08:05.900 --> 08:07.660
She's clever and full of ideas.

08:07.660 --> 08:09.140
You've mentioned her confinement

08:09.140 --> 08:10.630
countless times today.

08:10.630 --> 08:11.480
With that time,

08:11.490 --> 08:13.100
you might as well send the samples down.

08:16.700 --> 08:17.540
I'll go.

08:19.410 --> 08:20.370
After years of study,

08:20.730 --> 08:22.340
it's time to gain experience.

08:23.290 --> 08:24.810
You truly plan to go down?

08:25.700 --> 08:26.540
Then be careful.

08:26.540 --> 08:27.993
Help me open a few new trade routes.

08:29.540 --> 08:30.980
Fengchi, you...

08:32.300 --> 08:33.140
Lingbo,

08:33.580 --> 08:34.526
I've thought it through.

08:35.300 --> 08:36.730
Only by aiming high

08:36.730 --> 08:37.570
and becoming capable

08:38.130 --> 08:39.850
can I stand by your side to protect you

08:40.420 --> 08:41.420
and keep you safe.

09:00.580 --> 09:01.490
This is Hui's paper.

09:02.060 --> 09:03.300
The ink will last longer.

09:03.700 --> 09:04.940
If it's not enough, tell me.

09:05.340 --> 09:06.250
I'll buy more.

09:07.250 --> 09:09.730
You bring paper every three days.

09:10.300 --> 09:12.370
This is enough to last for two years.

09:14.300 --> 09:16.130
If sect affairs are busy,

09:16.130 --> 09:18.730
you need not come so often.

09:20.130 --> 09:20.970
It's no trouble.

09:49.100 --> 09:50.700
Master has confined me for a year.

09:51.220 --> 09:52.940
Though it seems harsh and heartless,

09:53.530 --> 09:54.530
I know

09:54.980 --> 09:56.610
he is calming the storm for me.

09:58.300 --> 09:59.250
During this time,

09:59.980 --> 10:01.940
I can write down

10:01.940 --> 10:02.886
my thoughts and records.

10:03.770 --> 10:05.250
When I emerge next year,

10:06.130 --> 10:07.220
I'll be a heroine once more.

10:09.420 --> 10:11.370
Master always praises you
for your quick mind.

10:12.250 --> 10:13.820
You truly understand his intentions.

10:15.180 --> 10:16.020
Yuzhi,

10:16.530 --> 10:18.700
do you know what kind of storybook
I intend to write?

10:20.700 --> 10:22.700
You must want to write about Miss Cai,

10:23.010 --> 10:23.980
Uncle Guo,

10:24.770 --> 10:27.340
and my grandfather.

10:27.980 --> 10:29.220
As for Lord Yin,

10:31.060 --> 10:32.730
I won't write any flattering words.

10:33.010 --> 10:33.980
If it's true,

10:34.530 --> 10:35.370
why not?

10:37.820 --> 10:38.770
Yuzhi,

10:39.420 --> 10:40.380
you're a true gentleman.

10:45.340 --> 10:46.820
A few days ago, Lingbo sent word back.

10:47.340 --> 10:48.180
In her letter,

10:48.530 --> 10:50.456
she wrote of all she saw and heard
with Fengchi.

10:51.060 --> 10:52.530
It sounded carefree and delightful.

10:54.370 --> 10:55.730
Lingbo has finally

10:56.180 --> 10:58.010
faced her heart.

11:02.010 --> 11:04.130
Yuzhi, do you know why I wish to leave?

11:06.530 --> 11:07.770
Because I dislike Cai Zhao.

11:09.980 --> 11:11.490
I dislike that she cares about nothing.

11:12.730 --> 11:14.770
I dislike that she took
your and Father's favor.

11:15.340 --> 11:16.940
I dislike that however I bullied her,

11:16.940 --> 11:18.610
she never took it to heart.

11:19.490 --> 11:21.940
I also dislike
that she could go alone for medicine.

11:23.770 --> 11:25.340
I dislike that she saw at a glance

11:25.340 --> 11:26.220
that Father was fake.

11:27.180 --> 11:29.890
I dislike that knowing Mu Qingyan
is the Chief of the demonic sect,

11:30.650 --> 11:32.530
she still saved him without hesitation.

11:32.940 --> 11:34.610
How can she be like that?

11:36.100 --> 11:38.060
How can she be so unrestrained

11:38.060 --> 11:39.220
and free?

11:42.010 --> 11:42.890
Lingbo,

11:44.390 --> 11:45.820
you needn't compare yourself to her.

11:45.820 --> 11:46.660
Yuzhi,

11:49.180 --> 11:50.253
I didn't understand before.

11:50.940 --> 11:53.060
But now I do.

11:54.850 --> 11:56.010
I don't dislike her.

11:56.940 --> 11:57.980
I envy her.

12:00.420 --> 12:01.340
The world is vast.

12:02.370 --> 12:03.940
One should live more freely.

12:04.610 --> 12:05.450
So,

12:06.420 --> 12:07.890
I'll do whatever I wish to do.

12:14.820 --> 12:15.730
Yuzhi,

12:18.010 --> 12:20.100
you are too calm and restrained.

12:20.580 --> 12:22.730
That's why you are overshadowed
by Mu Qingyan.

12:23.300 --> 12:24.370
In this life,

12:24.850 --> 12:26.180
one should live for oneself.

12:28.420 --> 12:29.420
The world is vast.

12:30.490 --> 12:31.730
Live by your heart.

12:52.420 --> 12:53.650
(The world is vast.)

12:55.250 --> 12:56.730
(Live by your heart.)

12:58.060 --> 12:59.220
Lingbo's story

12:59.820 --> 13:01.490
can become another storybook.

13:02.980 --> 13:03.940
Lingbo's courage

13:04.850 --> 13:06.530
has made Fengchi courageous too.

13:08.730 --> 13:10.180
If only one person is brave,

13:10.610 --> 13:11.770
it's likely useless.

13:36.730 --> 13:38.300
Thank you for saving my life.

13:40.490 --> 13:41.330
Sit.

13:45.580 --> 13:46.850
Why did Yu Hui want to kill you?

14:04.940 --> 14:05.780
Fengge,

14:06.250 --> 14:07.850
it was thanks to you again.

14:08.100 --> 14:09.250
You killed the Chief.

14:09.940 --> 14:11.340
His followers won't spare you.

14:12.610 --> 14:13.650
What are your plans?

14:14.130 --> 14:16.130
Once I find the one behind Nie Zhe,

14:16.850 --> 14:18.730
Li Sect is nothing to fear.

14:20.010 --> 14:21.490
Nie Zhe reached this point

14:21.980 --> 14:22.820
because of him.

14:23.100 --> 14:23.980
He manipulated Nie

14:24.490 --> 14:25.423
to refine corpse slaves

14:25.580 --> 14:26.700
and provoke the Six Sects.

14:27.370 --> 14:28.210
Yu,

14:29.250 --> 14:30.650
you must not follow Nie Zhe's path.

14:33.610 --> 14:34.450
Fengge,

14:34.980 --> 14:35.850
I'm hungry.

14:36.370 --> 14:37.370
Find some food.

14:49.370 --> 14:51.340
When I returned with food,

14:52.490 --> 14:54.530
someone else was inside.

14:54.980 --> 14:56.730
As long as you help me kill Mu Qingyan

14:56.730 --> 14:57.940
and avenge them,

14:57.940 --> 14:59.100
I'll do anything.

15:00.940 --> 15:01.780
Who is there?

15:10.130 --> 15:11.580
You know what to do.

15:12.650 --> 15:13.490
Yu.

15:17.770 --> 15:18.610
You...

15:24.180 --> 15:25.220
why?

15:25.770 --> 15:26.890
The Demonic Camp

15:26.890 --> 15:27.850
is gone.

15:28.700 --> 15:29.940
You are of no use to me now.

15:35.820 --> 15:36.660
Fengge,

15:37.940 --> 15:39.220
I'll remember you.

15:54.130 --> 15:55.180
He didn't know

15:55.980 --> 15:57.940
my heart is distinctive.

15:59.420 --> 16:00.850
It's on the other side.

16:02.250 --> 16:03.890
This stab can't take my life.

16:05.580 --> 16:07.220
Master once told me

16:08.490 --> 16:10.340
that however much you like someone,

16:10.770 --> 16:11.980
some secrets

16:12.610 --> 16:14.100
must never be revealed.

16:16.490 --> 16:17.580
I didn't expect

16:18.850 --> 16:20.490
those words to save me.

16:21.610 --> 16:23.250
Did you see the man in black's face?

16:23.460 --> 16:24.300
He wore a mask.

16:24.300 --> 16:25.140
His voice was deep.

16:25.850 --> 16:28.010
His martial arts were unfathomable.

16:28.610 --> 16:29.980
What he seeks

16:30.530 --> 16:31.820
is far more than Li Sect.

16:39.130 --> 16:40.940
Before, I was used by schemers,

16:40.940 --> 16:41.850
aiding evil.

16:42.370 --> 16:43.490
I nearly let Li Sect

16:43.490 --> 16:45.010
fall into the villains' hands.

16:45.610 --> 16:46.910
I have shamed Master's teachings.

16:47.650 --> 16:48.820
From this day forth,

16:49.820 --> 16:51.010
I pledge loyalty to you,

16:52.100 --> 16:52.940
to protect Li Sect

16:53.530 --> 16:54.650
and avenge myself.

16:58.530 --> 16:59.370
Rise.

17:15.700 --> 17:18.090
Pay closer attention
to those around you.

17:18.570 --> 17:19.410
I believe

17:20.010 --> 17:21.660
that without the Sevens Pill,

17:22.490 --> 17:24.380
your subordinates wouldn't betray you.

17:26.180 --> 17:27.530
Without testing,

17:28.730 --> 17:29.980
you can still have

17:30.570 --> 17:32.330
subordinates loyal to you.

17:37.330 --> 17:38.170
Young Master.

17:47.490 --> 17:48.380
I trust you.

18:27.490 --> 18:29.010
(Without the Jade Sunflower,)

18:29.010 --> 18:30.940
(no progress in the Ziwei Method.)

18:32.860 --> 18:35.490
He retrieved the saliva with my aunt

18:35.940 --> 18:37.530
and knew about the Jade Sunflower.

18:39.180 --> 18:41.530
He approached her with ulterior motives.

18:43.180 --> 18:45.530
(Did Mu Zhengyang practice
the Ziwei Method as well?)

19:00.380 --> 19:02.090
The wedding begins.

19:02.660 --> 19:03.980
Congratulations!

19:03.980 --> 19:06.900
Lay the carpets!

19:21.330 --> 19:24.010
Love begins prosperously!

19:26.570 --> 19:29.050
May you live in harmony

19:29.700 --> 19:32.660
and share old age together!

19:34.290 --> 19:35.180
Congratulations!

19:41.090 --> 19:44.490
The newlyweds kneel.

19:46.810 --> 19:48.380
First bow.

19:53.050 --> 19:54.660
Second bow.

19:56.770 --> 19:58.180
Third bow.

19:58.620 --> 19:59.810
Rise.

20:03.700 --> 20:05.980
The couple bows to each other.

20:12.290 --> 20:14.380
Thank the Young Master.

20:31.730 --> 20:32.570
A gift.

20:34.860 --> 20:35.860
Thanks, Young Master.

20:36.050 --> 20:36.890
Young Master,

20:37.220 --> 20:39.010
you gave Master You such a grand gift.

20:39.810 --> 20:41.050
When I married...

20:41.050 --> 20:42.010
Come on.

20:42.010 --> 20:43.050
You've married twice.

20:43.050 --> 20:45.530
Do you expect the Young Master
to send two gifts?

20:46.570 --> 20:47.940
Honey.

20:50.330 --> 20:51.420
The ceremony is complete.

20:54.380 --> 20:56.570
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

21:19.620 --> 21:21.090
Smiley.

21:21.090 --> 21:23.050
How did you know I wanted to eat Smiley?

21:23.290 --> 21:24.980
It was sent from the Hanhai Mountains.

21:25.530 --> 21:27.076
I heard they've been holding a wedding.

21:29.730 --> 21:30.730
A wedding?

21:31.330 --> 21:33.380
Master You insisted I deliver it to you.

21:33.770 --> 21:35.140
Xing did us a favor after all.

21:35.730 --> 21:37.103
We can't refuse her wedding sweets.

21:38.330 --> 21:40.420
So, it's You Guanyue and Xing's wedding.

21:44.050 --> 21:44.890
So sweet.

21:52.050 --> 21:52.890
Zhao.

21:56.380 --> 21:57.700
- I...
- Yuzhi,

21:59.050 --> 22:00.290
my ink is almost gone.

22:05.770 --> 22:06.610
I...

22:07.770 --> 22:08.940
I'll buy you more.

22:09.530 --> 22:11.050
Then thank you, Yuzhi.

22:11.810 --> 22:12.980
I've thought it through.

22:13.530 --> 22:15.140
From this round of bookshop earnings,

22:16.180 --> 22:17.490
I'll give you 20%.

22:23.770 --> 22:25.076
Then you should focus on writing.

22:26.010 --> 22:26.850
I'll take my leave.

22:28.090 --> 22:29.010
Goodbye.

22:46.900 --> 22:48.810
You want to ask about Zhengyang?

22:50.730 --> 22:51.570
After that,

22:51.770 --> 22:53.330
we only met that one time.

22:53.730 --> 22:54.700
That night,

22:54.940 --> 22:56.810
Zhengyang kept speaking of Pingshu,

22:57.730 --> 22:59.180
who was Ms. Cai.

22:59.700 --> 23:01.730
He said Ms. Cai was so good.

23:01.980 --> 23:04.180
He was truly happy that night,

23:04.180 --> 23:06.770
saying we'd live good days ahead,

23:06.770 --> 23:07.770
and told me to take care.

23:07.770 --> 23:09.140
Take care of what?

23:09.140 --> 23:10.335
He was the one who should stop

23:10.346 --> 23:12.412
risking his life in places
like the snow mountains.

23:12.980 --> 23:14.330
Other than the snow mountains,

23:14.330 --> 23:15.570
did he mention

23:15.570 --> 23:16.980
any other places he had been?

23:19.250 --> 23:20.980
Other places?

23:34.770 --> 23:35.610
Uncle Lei,

23:35.899 --> 23:36.888
what do you need with me?

23:36.940 --> 23:37.780
How

23:37.940 --> 23:38.780
has Zhao been lately?

23:39.220 --> 23:40.530
Do you miss her?

23:41.560 --> 23:42.766
Have you two made any progress?

23:46.140 --> 23:47.490
Zhao was injured

23:47.490 --> 23:48.420
and confined.

23:48.980 --> 23:50.533
She writes storybooks to ease her mood.

23:51.250 --> 23:52.810
Being able to proofread her manuscripts

23:52.810 --> 23:54.090
is enough for me.

23:54.090 --> 23:55.140
During this year,

23:55.660 --> 23:57.250
you're the only one who can be with her.

23:57.940 --> 23:59.140
And you only proofread?

24:00.380 --> 24:01.730
What do you mean?

24:02.420 --> 24:04.050
Your generation

24:04.050 --> 24:06.250
has nearly been ruined

24:06.250 --> 24:07.140
by so-called propriety.

24:07.860 --> 24:09.380
Your father may be reckless,

24:09.380 --> 24:11.140
but at least he has boldness.

24:11.940 --> 24:13.570
When it's time to act, he acts.

24:14.700 --> 24:16.010
Once her year of confinement ends,

24:16.700 --> 24:18.380
Zhao will return to Luoying Valley.

24:18.900 --> 24:19.810
You'll have no chance.

24:31.540 --> 24:33.980
(Right the ways of Jianghu;
clear my name)

24:33.980 --> 24:34.900
How is it?

24:36.010 --> 24:36.850
Not bad.

24:37.220 --> 24:38.060
It's done!

24:38.900 --> 24:40.220
Hurry and tell Xingjia.

24:40.220 --> 24:41.506
Have him inform Uncle Wordsmith

24:41.860 --> 24:43.090
to prepare for printing.

24:46.860 --> 24:47.700
Zhao,

24:48.140 --> 24:49.220
I have something to say.

24:50.250 --> 24:51.220
What is it, Yuzhi?

24:52.810 --> 24:53.580
In a few days,

24:53.591 --> 24:55.404
my brother will marry
Miss Yang of Siqi Sect.

24:56.010 --> 24:57.420
I must return to Guangtian Sect.

24:58.090 --> 24:59.490
Xiaolan

25:00.010 --> 25:01.620
is truly marrying your brother?

25:02.420 --> 25:03.260
Zhao,

25:05.730 --> 25:07.220
do you want to go with me?

25:14.490 --> 25:16.290
A few days ago, Han wrote to say

25:16.900 --> 25:19.490
he's taken a liking
to knocking wooden fish

25:20.220 --> 25:21.290
and wants to become a monk.

25:22.250 --> 25:23.140
So?

25:23.420 --> 25:24.260
So,

25:24.546 --> 25:25.840
the family line of Luoying Valley

25:26.010 --> 25:27.770
depends on me.

25:28.290 --> 25:30.420
Yuzhi, are you willing
to marry into my family?

25:30.770 --> 25:31.610
I'm willing.

25:32.290 --> 25:33.660
The child must take my surname.

25:34.180 --> 25:35.490
You're willing to accept that?

25:35.490 --> 25:36.330
I'm willing.

25:40.620 --> 25:41.530
But I'm not.

25:42.810 --> 25:43.940
Yuzhi, you are wonderful.

25:44.700 --> 25:46.380
Guangtian Sect is prominent.

25:46.900 --> 25:48.490
It's indeed a good match.

25:50.200 --> 25:51.050
But...

25:51.050 --> 25:52.860
I'm not Mu Qingyan.

25:52.860 --> 25:54.220
You are not Mu Qingyan,

25:55.420 --> 25:57.090
nor need you become him.

25:59.290 --> 26:00.220
When I was little,

26:00.220 --> 26:02.010
there was a toy I loved dearly.

26:02.620 --> 26:05.090
One day, I lost it by accident.

26:05.420 --> 26:07.250
My parents bought me many toys

26:07.250 --> 26:08.980
to cheer me up.

26:10.620 --> 26:11.620
Some were even better

26:11.620 --> 26:13.770
than the first one.

26:15.730 --> 26:17.050
But I didn't want them.

26:19.940 --> 26:21.250
Because

26:21.250 --> 26:23.050
I couldn't love them

26:23.700 --> 26:25.180
the way I loved the first.

26:28.380 --> 26:29.420
Yuzhi,

26:31.700 --> 26:32.570
I'm sorry.

26:49.940 --> 26:52.220
I can't replace your first toy.

26:53.140 --> 26:54.180
But what if one day,

26:54.900 --> 26:56.330
you no longer long for that toy

26:58.180 --> 26:59.730
and need a sword instead?

27:00.710 --> 27:01.570
Yuzhi...

27:01.570 --> 27:02.620
Zhao,

27:02.620 --> 27:03.460
we still have time.

27:05.380 --> 27:06.220
I can wait.

27:43.810 --> 27:44.650
What should we do?

27:51.810 --> 27:52.650
Lingbo,

27:53.140 --> 27:53.980
you go.

27:54.290 --> 27:55.130
I'll hold them off.

27:55.220 --> 27:56.486
If we fight, we fight together.

27:56.570 --> 27:58.290
I won't leave you alone.

27:58.290 --> 27:59.130
Go.

27:59.130 --> 28:00.050
Go!

28:00.490 --> 28:01.330
I won't.

28:02.180 --> 28:03.220
I won't!

28:04.490 --> 28:05.660
If you die,

28:06.900 --> 28:08.570
there is no meaning for me to live.

28:09.530 --> 28:11.050
I want us to be together forever.

28:17.730 --> 28:18.570
All right.

28:19.660 --> 28:21.220
We will be together forever.

28:49.530 --> 28:50.770
Lingbo's letter said

28:50.950 --> 28:52.543
someone from Huangsha Gang
went missing.

28:52.940 --> 28:54.530
She and Fengchi went to help search.

28:55.203 --> 28:56.165
But those missing people

28:56.176 --> 28:57.700
suddenly went mad and attacked them.

28:57.980 --> 28:59.010
From her description,

28:59.770 --> 29:01.290
they were surely corpse slaves.

29:01.290 --> 29:02.180
How is Lingbo?

29:02.810 --> 29:04.420
Fengchi protected her with his life.

29:04.700 --> 29:06.240
They escaped only when Mr. Song Xiuzhi

29:06.570 --> 29:07.570
arrived with men.

29:09.290 --> 29:10.220
Master,

29:10.220 --> 29:11.940
after Mu Qingyan became the Chief,

29:11.940 --> 29:13.490
he forbade refining corpse slaves.

29:13.810 --> 29:14.660
By logic,

29:15.620 --> 29:17.090
they should not reappear.

29:18.050 --> 29:20.700
Perhaps it's deceit.

29:21.090 --> 29:23.090
The demonic sect has done it before.

29:23.980 --> 29:24.980
This matter

29:24.980 --> 29:26.140
is too strange.

29:26.730 --> 29:28.180
I must go in person.

29:28.570 --> 29:29.410
Yuzhi,

29:29.940 --> 29:31.050
remain at Qingque Sect.

29:31.620 --> 29:32.460
Yes.

30:10.660 --> 30:11.700
I'm out.

30:14.730 --> 30:16.810
Congrats on completing confinement!

30:20.290 --> 30:21.250
Xingjia,

30:21.620 --> 30:22.460
after a year apart,

30:22.730 --> 30:23.810
you've grown plumper.

30:25.380 --> 30:27.700
I've labored for the sect's livelihood.

30:28.010 --> 30:29.420
I've clearly slimmed down.

30:31.570 --> 30:34.180
The Shanci Mushrooms
and orchids you brought back

30:34.660 --> 30:36.660
have all been planted
in the herbal field.

30:37.220 --> 30:38.620
I only planted them for fun.

30:39.330 --> 30:40.170
Who knew

30:40.570 --> 30:41.700
they would prove useful?

30:42.900 --> 30:45.860
After three days and nights of refining,

30:46.330 --> 30:47.170
I've finally

30:47.420 --> 30:49.090
produced

30:49.530 --> 30:50.620
this

30:50.620 --> 30:51.620
Invincible

30:51.620 --> 30:52.490
Corpse Breaker.

30:54.490 --> 30:57.290
Xingjia, that name is truly...

30:58.220 --> 30:59.570
Amazing.

30:59.570 --> 31:00.530
I think so too.

31:02.730 --> 31:04.490
Can it truly cure corpse slaves?

31:04.490 --> 31:06.220
As long as the poison is not deep,

31:06.220 --> 31:07.620
they'll recover at once.

31:07.980 --> 31:09.660
Once Master finds their whereabouts,

31:10.010 --> 31:11.290
we can save everyone.

31:11.620 --> 31:12.940
Corpse slaves move in secrecy.

31:13.660 --> 31:14.620
Master has no news yet.

31:15.180 --> 31:16.090
Nie Zhe is dead.

31:17.380 --> 31:18.530
Could these corpse slaves

31:19.180 --> 31:20.490
be the work of the man in black?

31:20.860 --> 31:21.980
I think

31:21.980 --> 31:23.010
he likely knows

31:23.010 --> 31:25.180
how to refine them.

31:25.180 --> 31:26.150
In fact, this past year,

31:26.161 --> 31:28.427
Master asked me to investigate
members of the Six Sects,

31:28.660 --> 31:29.620
including Uncle Li.

31:31.570 --> 31:33.140
But I found nothing unusual.

31:33.700 --> 31:35.980
The man in black seems
to have vanished into thin air.

31:35.980 --> 31:38.220
If he's behind the corpse slaves,

31:38.220 --> 31:39.060
what does he want?

31:39.730 --> 31:40.660
At the very least,

31:40.660 --> 31:43.050
they wouldn't appear at Guangtian Sect
without reason.

31:52.090 --> 31:53.380
Where's this carrier pigeon from?

31:53.380 --> 31:54.570
I worried for Father's safety

31:54.570 --> 31:55.700
and wrote home.

31:56.050 --> 31:56.940
This must be the reply.

32:04.050 --> 32:04.900
Something's wrong.

32:08.140 --> 32:09.660
Father is in secluded cultivation.

32:09.660 --> 32:10.900
All is well in the sect.

32:12.290 --> 32:13.420
What's wrong?

32:13.420 --> 32:15.250
With corpse slaves reappearing,

32:15.250 --> 32:16.330
how can Father remain

32:16.330 --> 32:17.170
in seclusion?

32:19.293 --> 32:20.593
I must return to Guangtian Sect.

32:20.900 --> 32:21.900
I'll go with you.

32:21.900 --> 32:22.940
I feel this matter

32:22.940 --> 32:24.490
is linked to the man in black.

32:25.330 --> 32:26.180
Perhaps

32:26.180 --> 32:28.220
this is our chance to catch him.

32:28.940 --> 32:30.620
My year of confinement has ended.

32:31.940 --> 32:33.140
Let's depart at once.

32:33.140 --> 32:33.980
All right.

32:44.010 --> 32:45.210
Other than the snow mountains,

32:45.330 --> 32:46.250
did he mention

32:46.530 --> 32:47.860
any other places he had been?

32:48.180 --> 32:49.140
Vaguely,

32:49.700 --> 32:51.980
something about Blood...

32:53.770 --> 32:54.620
Marsh Forest?

32:54.860 --> 32:59.020
(Guangtian Sect, Blood Marsh Forest)

33:09.180 --> 33:10.020
Young Master,

33:10.980 --> 33:11.900
near Guangtian Sect,

33:12.220 --> 33:13.339
corpse slaves have appeared.

33:13.940 --> 33:14.780
Also,

33:14.940 --> 33:16.900
Miss Cai has left Qingque Sect.

33:21.140 --> 33:22.533
Her year of confinement has ended.

33:23.570 --> 33:25.420
It's time for her to return
to Luoying Valley.

33:25.420 --> 33:26.380
Miss Cai

33:26.980 --> 33:28.900
went to Guangtian Sect with Song Yuzhi.

33:32.090 --> 33:33.250
Not my business.

33:37.980 --> 33:39.660
(Blood Marsh Forest)

33:39.660 --> 33:44.860
(Guangtian Sect)

33:44.860 --> 33:47.780
(Timely Chamber)

33:47.810 --> 33:48.650
Xiuzhi.

33:48.980 --> 33:49.820
Yuzhi,

33:50.250 --> 33:51.090
why are you back?

33:51.570 --> 33:52.410
What's wrong?

33:52.700 --> 33:53.660
What happened?

33:56.420 --> 33:57.260
I must see Father.

33:57.470 --> 33:58.330
Do not enter.

33:58.330 --> 33:59.570
I must see him.

34:00.900 --> 34:02.700
Xiuzhi, you are injured.

34:03.090 --> 34:04.770
I hurt myself while practicing.

34:05.200 --> 34:06.090
Xiuzhi,

34:06.090 --> 34:07.010
what is going on?

34:08.260 --> 34:10.130
Is it related to the corpse slaves?

34:10.490 --> 34:11.330
Master Xiuzhi.

34:12.940 --> 34:13.900
Master Yuzhi,

34:13.900 --> 34:14.740
you're back.

34:16.300 --> 34:17.170
The Huangsha Gang

34:17.170 --> 34:18.900
has summoned Lord Yang of Siqi Sect.

34:18.900 --> 34:20.010
Go take a look.

34:20.010 --> 34:20.860
Let's go together.

34:22.300 --> 34:25.540
(Timely Chamber)

34:25.780 --> 34:26.620
Uncle Song,

34:27.340 --> 34:28.820
though the Huangsha Gang is weak,

34:29.300 --> 34:30.535
my father-in-law never bullied

34:30.546 --> 34:31.690
the weak in decades.

34:32.260 --> 34:33.340
As long as he had breath,

34:33.860 --> 34:35.860
he aided those in peril.

34:35.860 --> 34:36.780
Who would've thought

34:36.780 --> 34:38.650
he'd die at the hands of his mates?

34:39.530 --> 34:41.090
Senior,

34:41.090 --> 34:42.300
please uphold justice for him.

34:42.610 --> 34:44.860
Mr. Huang was upright.

34:45.130 --> 34:47.050
If he suffered injustice,

34:47.050 --> 34:49.010
we will seek justice.

34:49.010 --> 34:50.130
Who is he?

34:50.650 --> 34:51.980
He is Father's cousin,

34:52.380 --> 34:53.260
my grand uncle.

34:53.499 --> 34:55.259
He holds the highest seniority
in my family.

34:55.270 --> 34:56.110
Lord Yang.

34:59.570 --> 35:01.050
Why hasn't Song Shijun come?

35:01.050 --> 35:02.530
Father is in seclusion.

35:02.530 --> 35:04.570
I'm temporarily in charge.

35:04.570 --> 35:06.090
Whatever you wish to say,

35:06.090 --> 35:07.300
speak to me.

35:07.300 --> 35:08.140
In seclusion?

35:09.380 --> 35:11.420
Is he truly unable to come out

35:11.420 --> 35:13.530
or too guilty to appear?

35:13.530 --> 35:14.940
Mind your words.

35:14.940 --> 35:16.570
What guilt does my father bear?

35:16.570 --> 35:17.530
Very well.

35:17.530 --> 35:19.170
Then, before everyone,

35:19.170 --> 35:20.380
I'll speak plainly.

35:20.740 --> 35:21.650
My father-in-law,

35:22.170 --> 35:23.780
Leader Huang of Huangsha Gang,

35:24.340 --> 35:25.900
retired from Jianghu years ago

35:26.570 --> 35:28.170
and lived quietly with his family.

35:28.570 --> 35:29.900
Yet Song Shijun

35:30.170 --> 35:32.210
coveted the secrecy
of his mountain retreat

35:32.490 --> 35:34.090
to refine corpse slaves.

35:34.530 --> 35:36.076
When my father-in-law discovered this,

35:36.300 --> 35:38.090
Song Shijun silenced them all,

35:38.420 --> 35:40.740
slaughtering the old and young

35:40.740 --> 35:42.300
of the gang.

35:44.210 --> 35:45.050
Lord Yang,

35:45.300 --> 35:46.340
words alone are not proof.

35:47.210 --> 35:48.170
Do you have evidence?

35:48.170 --> 35:49.340
After the massacre,

35:49.900 --> 35:52.050
I examined the sword wounds.

35:52.340 --> 35:54.780
All died by Guangtian sword moves.

35:55.490 --> 35:56.900
The Six Sects are allies.

35:56.900 --> 35:59.130
We share knowledge.

35:59.130 --> 36:01.170
Imitating Guangtian sword marks

36:01.170 --> 36:02.010
is not difficult.

36:02.340 --> 36:03.180
Of course,

36:03.490 --> 36:04.780
I wouldn't accuse lightly

36:04.780 --> 36:06.610
based on sword moves alone.

36:06.980 --> 36:09.050
But Song Shijun slipped once

36:09.300 --> 36:10.780
and left a survivor.

36:11.090 --> 36:11.940
Sha Tian'er,

36:18.650 --> 36:20.420
show them your wound.

36:24.260 --> 36:25.340
All know

36:25.610 --> 36:27.210
Lord Song's sword moves are unique.

36:27.570 --> 36:28.820
The wounds are unseen at first,

36:29.050 --> 36:29.890
and later,

36:30.820 --> 36:32.170
the scar blooms like a flower.

36:33.050 --> 36:34.820
Senior, please examine it.

36:53.090 --> 36:53.930
Indeed,

36:54.530 --> 36:57.260
it's a wound from Shijun's sword.

36:57.570 --> 36:58.740
What proof is that?

36:59.530 --> 37:00.740
Everyone knows

37:00.740 --> 37:03.090
his sword style is ornate.

37:03.090 --> 37:04.050
Though flashy,

37:04.050 --> 37:05.300
it's not hard

37:06.050 --> 37:07.090
to learn.

37:07.380 --> 37:08.220
Cai Zhao,

37:08.650 --> 37:10.050
this is not your place to speak.

37:10.050 --> 37:11.260
If we speak of fairness,

37:11.820 --> 37:12.820
anyone may speak.

37:15.610 --> 37:16.543
I arrived just in time.

37:16.860 --> 37:18.210
How could I not join?

37:22.130 --> 37:22.980
Sha Tian'er,

37:24.530 --> 37:25.380
tell us

37:26.260 --> 37:27.690
how Lord Song wounded you.

37:28.380 --> 37:29.610
My master, Leader Huang,

37:30.050 --> 37:31.820
heard villagers were disappearing.

37:32.420 --> 37:33.420
We learned

37:33.740 --> 37:35.090
remnants of the Nie faction

37:35.090 --> 37:36.463
had sought refuge at Guangtian Sect

37:36.710 --> 37:37.570
and offered

37:37.570 --> 37:39.530
the method to refine corpse slaves

37:39.530 --> 37:40.820
to Song Shijun.

37:41.420 --> 37:43.340
When the secret leaked,

37:43.860 --> 37:45.260
he slaughtered the Huangsha Gang

37:45.260 --> 37:46.940
to conceal it.

37:48.900 --> 37:49.980
I survived

37:50.420 --> 37:51.610
only by feigning death.

37:51.900 --> 37:53.900
That is only your word.

37:56.380 --> 37:58.170
Song Shijun even hurt

37:58.170 --> 37:59.050
his own son.

37:59.060 --> 38:00.130
Isn't that proof?

38:00.650 --> 38:01.490
No.

38:02.210 --> 38:03.050
Xiuzhi,

38:03.050 --> 38:04.300
what happened?

38:04.300 --> 38:05.650
Was it truly Father?

38:05.650 --> 38:06.690
It was not Father.

38:06.690 --> 38:08.490
I'll answer for him.

38:08.490 --> 38:09.740
Xiuzhi

38:09.740 --> 38:10.940
saved Miss Qi and Mr. Dai

38:10.940 --> 38:12.820
from corpse slaves

38:12.820 --> 38:13.670
and uncovered

38:13.670 --> 38:15.530
Song Shijun's plot.

38:15.530 --> 38:18.340
Song Shijun forced Xiuzhi to hide it,

38:18.340 --> 38:19.820
but Xiuzhi refused,

38:19.820 --> 38:22.570
so Song Shijun tried to silence him.

38:22.570 --> 38:23.900
I wondered why sounds

38:23.900 --> 38:26.050
of fighting came from his chamber.

38:26.050 --> 38:27.170
I see.

38:28.130 --> 38:30.170
What misfortune.

38:31.090 --> 38:31.930
Xiuzhi,

38:32.170 --> 38:33.690
is this true?

38:36.780 --> 38:37.620
Uncle Pang,

38:37.900 --> 38:38.740
you tell us.

38:39.900 --> 38:41.260
I don't know.

38:41.940 --> 38:43.130
When I returned,

38:44.340 --> 38:45.650
I saw Master Xiuzhi

38:45.650 --> 38:46.610
fighting the Lord.

38:46.980 --> 38:47.820
After that,

38:48.170 --> 38:49.570
the Lord entered seclusion.

38:50.010 --> 38:50.850
Yuzhi,

38:51.420 --> 38:52.900
Father had a momentary lapse.

38:52.900 --> 38:53.940
Do not blame him.

38:58.780 --> 38:59.620
Father,

38:59.710 --> 39:00.570
why have you come out?

39:00.570 --> 39:01.420
Father.

39:01.420 --> 39:02.530
Song Shijun,

39:03.210 --> 39:05.380
I want you to pay with blood!

39:08.640 --> 39:19.300
=Generation to Generation=

39:38.060 --> 39:42.470
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

39:43.035 --> 39:47.650
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

39:47.990 --> 39:52.555
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

39:53.080 --> 39:57.380
♪Free to wander in the world♪

40:00.325 --> 40:05.025
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

40:05.550 --> 40:09.840
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

40:10.500 --> 40:14.530
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

40:14.845 --> 40:19.970
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

40:20.545 --> 40:25.355
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

40:25.570 --> 40:29.740
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

40:30.465 --> 40:34.400
♪I freely roam in the world♪

40:34.900 --> 40:40.175
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

41:02.905 --> 41:08.035
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

41:08.400 --> 41:12.770
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

41:13.035 --> 41:17.165
♪I freely roam in the world♪

41:17.350 --> 41:22.925
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
